" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 593px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Etonogestrel implant",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 573px; height: 265px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Implanon&reg; is 40 mm in length and 2 mm in diameter. It is composed of a solid core of Evatane&reg; with the crystals of etonogestrel imbedded within the core. Surrounding the core is a thin layer of evatane (0.06 mm thick) that controls the rate which etonogestrel is released. The rigidity of the implant pertains to its ease of removal and resistance to fracture during removal.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
